Ver0.1 > 1907071425+8
Removes the /politics and /philosophy forum pages, as well as Popular Forum Posts in those categories.

Install:
0. Install the Tampermonkey extension and open the Dashboard.
1. Go to Utilities > URL.
2. Type in the following: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hpgbproductions/remove-bad-forums/master/remove%20bad%20forums
3. Click Import and Install
Changes will be seen in Forums. Works for both the old site and Eclipse as they have the same Forums HTML.
